    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "We don't have multi-index yet in production. We're using server-side rendering, and, in order of appearance:\r\n\r\n- `connectSearchBox` for the search bar\r\n- `connectStateResults` for tracking purposes\r\n- `connectHits` for the search results\r\n- `connectPagination` for the pagination\r\n- `Configure` component\r\n\r\nI'll see if I can reproduce in another environment, but so far haven't been able to. ",
